Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:24.62,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,460)\pos(32,270)}「某位少女的假日」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧斯拉  霧斯拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音她在隱瞞著霧斯拉的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢幻的自製電影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.76,0:02:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘飛碟對戰霧彌湖町的大怪獸霧斯拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和怪獸先生對戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全想像不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛碟射出光線
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將湖劈成兩半
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光線
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}光線
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  這部電影似乎在哪裡見過…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西數量少到只留下一份作為資料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都還沒看過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但汐音卻不還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我好像在哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電影裡絕對藏著霧斯拉的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音她打算將它占為己有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能有這種事的  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道霧斯拉的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾光線
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到汐音  將秘密公之於眾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道現在就出發嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小春要看店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.39,0:03:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  霧斯拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  難道被討厭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能明白我感情的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連你都拋棄我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會暴露的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音  走進便利店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.22,0:04:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香快去監視她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音是個貪吃鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然好可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧斯拉是個貪吃鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多吃的  她待會要去見霧斯拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧斯拉是甜黨？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾也喜歡吃甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來汐音總是來霧彌湖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  我之前就覺得可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是霧斯拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  是飛碟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她似乎想去那個島
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是電影裡呼喚霧斯拉的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她打算把霧斯拉呼喚出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能見到怪獸先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  好想快點見到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧  霧斯拉就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  果然和我想的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電影裡就是像這樣和霧斯拉通信的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音為了不讓別人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷地將霧斯拉叫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將食物送給它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大怪獸先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這邊看的話  看不清呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾  到妳出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經喬裝過了  沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧斯拉怎麼可能真的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳買了大量的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我吃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥  什麼  什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是我吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.21,0:08:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很愛吃啊  有什麼奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音很喜歡砂糖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼電影呢  為什麼一直借著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個是我的自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住  我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想看霧斯拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大怪獸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼妳有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我爸爸的收藏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來以前看過的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:08:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢  柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今的辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘎噢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.16,0:09:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我  霧斯拉
